CIS5
The tall figure stands at least 7 feet and is fully dressed in a black robe. It holds a tall straight staff topped with a red jewel, and its face is hidden. It stands, silent with its attention to you, but stays passive.
"Death beckons you with its grim implement. Embrace its cold grasp and speak 'It is I, friend, welcome me' before its front door, and you will be invited into its kingdom."
"I need not possessions!" the figure screeches.
How very rude that would be.